<div class="mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<div class="shortdescription nomobile noexcerpt noprint searchaux" style="display:none">American soldier, statesman, teacher, and author. Key figure in Vietnam War policy.</div>
<p class="mw-empty-elt">
</p>
